        auctioneer - The user that placed the Sculpture on auction.
        title - The Title of the Sculpture.
        creator - The Creator of the Sculpture.
        artCreationYear - The Creation Year of the Sculpture.
        reservePrice - The Reserve Price of the Sculpture.
        numBidsAllowed - The Maximum Number of Bids a Sculpture can have.
        width - The Width Dimension of the Sculpture.
        height - The Height Dimension of the Sculpture.
        depth - The Depth Dimension of the Sculpture.
        material - The Material of the Sculpture.
        newArt - The boolean value that sets the Sculpture as new to the System.
        onAuction - The boolean value that sets the Sculpture to on auction.
